Salvatore Ferragamo S.p.A. - Wikipedia





















 






Salvatore Ferragamo S.p.A.

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia
  (Redirected from Ferragamo)

					Jump to:					navigation, 					search


Salvatore Ferragamo S.p.A.





Type

Public, S.p.A.


Traded as
BIT: SFER


Industry
Fashion


Founded
Florence, Italy (1928)


Founder
Salvatore Ferragamo


Headquarters
Florence, Italy



Area served

Worldwide



Key people

Ferruccio Ferragamo (Chairman)
Eraldo Poletto (CEO)


Products
Shoes, leather goods, clothing


Revenue
€1,438 million (2016)



Operating income

 €261 million (2016)


Profit
€198 million (2016)


